QuestData.Title: Lost Lumberjacks
QuestData.Description: Shelly and her crew haven't returned from Gloomshade Grove.$b$bIt's been days... I hope everything is okay.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find out what happened to Shelly and the missing lumberjacks.
QuestData.RewardText: This is one of the pack mules Shelly and her crew took to Gloomshade Grove.
